<p>The first tower launching at Pine and Glen will be 45 storeys with one to three bedroom condos. Pine and Glen is perfectly situated at the corner of Glen Drive and Pinetree across from Lincoln Skytrain Station. It is steps from Coquitlam Centre Mall and urban amenities and it central to Douglas College, 6 elementary, middle and high schools and within a short walk to Lafarge Lake, Town Centre Park and the West Coast Express.</p>
<p>Enjoy 90,000 sqft of indoor and outdoor amenities space including a 5,000 sqft fitness facility, spin studio, yoga room and steam room, indoor and outdoor pools and hot tubs, oversized entertainment lounge with two Chef’s kitchens, outdoor BBQ and dining areas and a children’s playground.</p>
